# beads (br) — git handling for the .beads/ workspace.
#
# Allowlist form: ignore everything br generates locally, then re-include only
# the files meant to be shared. Upstream's denylist .gitignore "keeps changing
# too frequently" as new volatile files appear (steveyegge/beads#919); an
# allowlist stays correct without edits when br adds new local state.
#
# Committed (shared source of truth):
#   issues.jsonl  — the canonical issue export; merges cleanly in git
#   config.yaml   — shared project config (issue prefix, defaults)
#   routes.jsonl  — cross-project prefix routing, if used
# Ignored (local / per-machine / runtime):
#   beads.db*, *.lock, last-touched, *.tmp  — sqlite db + locks + scratch
#   .br_history/  — local history snapshots
#   daemon.*      — background daemon log / pid / lock
#   metadata.json — workspace-local db/export paths
#   .local_version — per-machine schema version
*
!issues.jsonl
!config.yaml
!routes.jsonl
!.gitignore
